descriptionHTML:
This is a simple watchface listing and link to google play app.
You can easily find our latest watchfaces for Android Wear.

Round Android Wear Watch target devices
- LG Watch Urbane 2nd
- HUAWEI Watch
- Casio WSD-F10
- Moto 360 2nd edition
- Fossil Q Founder
- Moto 360
- LG Watch Urbane
- LG G Watch R


Rectangle Android Wear Watch target devices
- Gear Live(Samusung)
- LG G Watch (LG)
- SmartWatch3 (Sony)
- Zen Watch (ASUS)
- Zen Watch2 (ASUS)

Enjoy stylish wearable life with our WatchFaces!
comments: Not updating weather :( I have moto360 and Nexus6 but faces with weather are not updating :(
Excellent Love being updated when new faces are available.
The Best (Moto360) You guys have the best watch faces on the play store keep it up.

IMO, This is the best watch face app So, I know it sucks to have to pay for faces, but a dollar per face really isn't that bad. I mean if you download a face just to realize you don't like it, just refund it. ALSO, you can change up the brightness, colors, °C/°F etc without the trouble of editing a bunch of crap.   Easy to navigate through since it's all categorized from moto360, LG G-R, and Square face watches,  etc.
Great Love it, perfect for Moto360. Have one complaint temperature is always 10 to15 degrees lower than actual
